Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This special video has been provided to all of you by Shounen Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you watch TV, please brighten\Nthe room and don't sit too close to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you forgot already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promised to lend you my manga the other day, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only twenty-four volumes anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only twenty-four?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can return them to me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, when you want to return them, do it a few at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carrying the entire set is pretty tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:17.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You could have brought\Na few at a time too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great detectives read manga too, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading can help you relax sometimes, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't become too enchanted with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally got a copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dream Station Bug,\N"Kamen Yaiba III: The Three Wizards"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, the game is set in a magical land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the old witch appear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go play it at Conan's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? My house again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your house is the Detective Boys' secret hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A secret hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you wish to know what's in your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the old witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still a spunky seventeen-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, what's with the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crystal ball is floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must really be a magic ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{My family has passed this magic ball from generation to generation.}This mystical orb has been passed down\Nin my family from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It answers whatever questions I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, mystical orb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you'd like to say to the boy with the glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.77,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At the place where thou shalt\Nmeet a tiger, a vulture and a giant frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thou must be ready to solve whatever comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vulture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A giant frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case, you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sh-She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really was an old...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about the prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Other than the fortune-telling,\Nthere's something else that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, we have clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, you want me to protect\Nthe treasure sword mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in this announcement from Kaitou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure you can defeat Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tonight at 8 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall enter your noble home\Nto retrieve your treasure sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, can't let down my guard for even a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, now that I,\NMouri Kogoro, am on the job,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not only will I protect your treasure sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will catch this Kaitou Kid at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? Come to think of it, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where have I seen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't need your kind of help here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're talking about Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiddo-schmiddo, your inept\Nassistance would be completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll protect the sword ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, don't come crying to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just dealing with these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These men? Aren't these policemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sayaka, who are these people behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and his daughter Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought they might be helpful to protect the sword from Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, just a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{This grandma is harder to deal with than Kid, right?}That grandma seems much tougher than Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secure the perimeter of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go inside, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, who is this Kanchou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a lowly thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will give him what he deserves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Yaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:03.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you don't look like Kamen Yaiba at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not Kamen Yaiba, I'm Kurogane Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's Kamen Yaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where the kids went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably playing around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mine Raizou, the head of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter Ran,\Nand our house guest, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that my wife and daughter invited you here on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My family and I are all students of kendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you see, when Kid appears,\Nhe'll find the tables have turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, please rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kid is arrested, we can have a little something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty big yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could play hide-and-seek here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, ribbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a vulture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Kid? Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vulture...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giant frog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not Kid then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NKagetora, Shonosuke, Gerozaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're scaring the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagetora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shonosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerozaimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're this kid's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, they're just pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gave us a fright for nothing.{So much fuss over nothing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is the place that the prediction was talking about.{It's the place from the prediction.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what on earth is this strange feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, those little kids {with}and their false alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Y-Yo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm Kurogane Kenjuurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is this treasure sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't know\Nwhere it is, Uncle can't protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bai Ganr?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I drank it before,\NI returned to my original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told you we don't need\Na detective's help protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, do you drink that liquor often?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I use this liquor in various herbal treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have a little bit of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret medicine that's been passed down in our family from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can cure any disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah, }Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll admit it doesn't taste very good,\Nbut I can guarantee it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink it all in one gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My body is burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe something is about to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "one more"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not what you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only lost sight of you for a moment,\Nand look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drinking alcohol when you're still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tell you, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be like my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ko-go-rou; go = five
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ken-juu-rou; juu = ten
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm Kenjuurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juugo-rou; juugo = fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And together we're Juugorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Kid should appear in 5 minutes.}Kid said he would arrive in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone take your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a large house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this is going to be even more worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me, Kaitou Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, where could that sword be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hurts, ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make such a fuss over nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, is this a house of monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I should get my work done quickly and leave this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're Kaitou Kid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It will make a mess of\Nyour pretty face, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much trouble,\NI'd like to know where the sword is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's in the kendo dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They have a dojo here at their house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get any closer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toss this bamboo sword away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful flower is more\Nfitting for a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, madam, if you will excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you, you lousy thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}C'mon, another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid! How dare you bewitch my wife and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the most charming person I have met this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, your charms won't work on my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't have a chance with this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right, that medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's possible with this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's starting, it's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, hold yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi Ran, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How've you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...duplicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mustache? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kid! You've disguised himself as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kid is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's within my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did they hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see you, sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you give me that treasure sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Kanchou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kanchou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kaitou, you pinhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're skilled, Kanchou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kaitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the sword, pinhead{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! I have to do something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe if I drink a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did he run to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Hattori... Hattori!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{How dare you!}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:48.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jirokichi, the Japanese Robin Hood who was a theif in 1800's Japan\N(nicknamed Nezumi Kozo, "Rat Boy")\Nwho stole from the rich and gave to the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must say, you're splendid. You remind me of that rat boy thief, Jirokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not some chivalrous thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long, pinhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get him, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:13.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what's this strange feeling bothering me since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I understand everything!{I got it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Kurogane Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready{ for the assault}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what pretty fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could that sword be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the treasure sword\Nthat Kid tried to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now I return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that Yaiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, Yaiba did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kudo Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous high school detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, I've been bothered by a strange premonition since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I finally understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} isn't wearing her usual\Nhead scarf, instead she's wearing a ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 10-yen bald spot on Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s\Nhair should be on the right side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today it's on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} doesn't have the freckles he always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two locks of hair he always has dangling in front have become three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her bangs are parted differently than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up or you won't be ready when everyone comes to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See what happens when you read manga late into the night? You can't get up on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get ready, I need to clear the breakfast table.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just a dream...
